                            <li>  Collected for legitimate purposes</li>
                            <li> Accurate and up to date</li>
                            <li>Adequate and relevant </li>
                            <li>  Protected against unauthorized access</li>
                            <li>  Retained only as necessary</li>
                            <li> Managed transparently</li>
                        </ul>
                   
                    <h6>  3.4 Categories of Student Data </h6>
                    <p> Student data may include: </p>
                        <ul> 
                            <li> Personal identification details</li>
                            <li>  Academic performance records</li>
                            <li> Examination scripts</li>
                            <li> Attendance records</li>
                            <li> Online learning activity</li>
                            <li>  Financial information</li>
                            <li> Biometric data where applicable</li>
                            <li> Health or accessibility information where voluntarily provided</li>
                            <li> Disciplinary records</li>
