                    <h6>  3.5 Collection and Use of Student Data </h6>
                    <p> Student data shall only be collected for legitimate educational purposes, including: </p>
                        <ul> 
                            <li>Admissions </li>
                            <li>  Academic administration</li>
                            <li> Course delivery</li>
                            <li> Examinations</li>
                            <li> Certification</li>
                            <li> Student welfare</li>
                            <li>Regulatory compliance </li>
                            <li> Research and quality improvement</li>
