                    <p> Access to student information shall be restricted to authorized personnel only. </p>
                    <p> <i> Authorized personnel must: </i></p>
                        <ul> 
                            <li> Maintain confidentiality </li>
                            <li> Use information only for approved purposes</li>
                            <li> Follow institutional security procedures</li>
                            <li> Protect login credentials</li>
                        </ul>
                    
