                    <p> The Institute shall implement reasonable safeguards for online learning systems, including: </p>
                        <ul> 
                            <li> Password-protected accounts</li>
                            <li>User authentication </li>
                            <li>  Secure learning platforms</li>
                            <li>  Encrypted data transmission where appropriate</li>
